'''Girgire ama Burjiko''' ({{lang-en|hearth}}; {{lang-ar|كانون (موقد)}}) waa aalad ka samaysan [[dhoobo]] la xarakeeyay  ama dhagax la qoray taasi oo loo isticmaalo in lagu karsado [[cunto|cuntada]], shido uunsiga, fooxa, bourtka iyo dhamaan noocyada bukhuurka ee la shido.
Noocyo badan oo kala duwan ayaa jira kuwaasi oo loo isticmaalo siyaabo kala duwan, sida '''[[Burjiko|Burjikada]],''' '''Idinka''' ama '''Dabqaadka''' iyo  '''kubo-kubo''' (dhagax qoran loo sameeyey qaabka feerada dharka oo inta la kululeeyo meelo jirka ka mida lagu qandiiriyo) laakiin kuwa ugu isticmaalka badan waa girgiraha ama ([[Burjiko]]) oo qaarkood dhego leh, kuwo kale aan lahayn wax dheg ah, kaasi oo laga sameeyay [[dhoobo]] ama dhagax la qoray. dhagaxa girgiraha ayaa waxaa caan ku ah gobolka '''[[Galguduud|galgaduud]]''' gaar ahaan magaalada [[ceelbuur]]<ref>http://www.somalinet.com/forums/viewtopic.php?t=350274</ref> iyo nawaaxigeeda, waana meesha ugu badan ee soo saarta burjikada iyo wixii la halmaala.<ref>https://celgaras.wordpress.com/2013/06/17/barro-taariikhda-ceelbuur-gal-gaduud/</ref> hawsha burjikada samaynteeda ah ayaan loo adeegsan wax qalab iyo mishin midna<ref>http://www.somalinet.com/forums/viewtopic.php?t=350274</ref>, dadka degaanka ayaa soo waday hawsha burjiko samayska sanado badan.<ref>http://www.somalinet.com/forums/viewtopic.php?t=332846</ref>

dhagaxa laga sameeyo burjikada ayaa ah dhagax cad waxaana loo yaqaan '''quarry'''<ref>[[:en:Quarry|https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Quarry]]</ref> ama<ref>http://www.mindat.org/min-3621.html</ref> '''Sepiolite'''<ref>[[:en:Sepiolite#cite_note-4|https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sepiolite#cite_note-4]]</ref>

==Isticmaalka==
[[File:Modern Dabqaad.jpg|thumb|left|100px|Girgireyaasha casriga ah]]
Girgiraha waxaa laga isticmaala dhamaan xaafadaha bulshada [[Soomaaliya|Soomaaliyeed]], waxayna ka mid tahay [[dhaqan Soomaali|dhaqanka dadka Soomaalida]].

==Samayska==

Sida caadiga ah dhamaan girigireha  waxa laga sameeyaa dhagax dhulka laga qodo ka dibna la qoro ilaa loo ekaysiiyo wixii looga baahnaa inuu noqdo sida burjiko ama dabqaad.<ref>Abdullahi, pp.98-99</ref>

Bulsho weynta Soomaaliyeed ee ku dhaqan wadanada [[qurbe|qurbaha]] waxay aad u codsadaan in loo soo diro dabqaadka. maadaama uu ka mid yahay dhaqanka soomaalida soo jireenka ah si ay guryaha ugu uunsadaan ama ugu qaacsadaan,

{{-}}

==Noocyo kale==

Girgireha waxaa aad ugu qaab iyo samays dhow girgire loo yaqaano ''mabkhara'', kaasi oo laga isticmaalo [[Carabi|gayiga Carabta]].

